te><br />\n仲有石澳..<br />\n<br />\n上面果d去過哂, 好撚悶"},{"pid":"2bab88a731d75481cfdb5024fa97216227f3fdd5","tid":378221,"uid":22402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:52:29.000Z","msg":"唔開心反而會狂踩油直奔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26ceacfcea3d7b24535626d0abd1083d6363a4f","tid":378221,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:19:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你都好, 起碼有錢養車<br />\n我都好想有部, 但基層收入, 買部2手每月比幾千閒錢去養都冇能力</blockquote><br />\n我都係萬頭窮撚，月月清。玩車呢d都係玩一年半載了左個心願就賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好羨慕d frd有屋企車/村屋泊車唔洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實平均計埋保險牌費保養，點平都3-5k一個月，如果你供埋車，一個月成皮野支出"},{"pid":"89b6c4bbeedf67699b97d1135616cd8002cebd4c","tid":378221,"uid":131241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:23:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>十二點後晚清水灣係世界級</blockquote><br />\n好多mk車..</blockquote><br />\n清水灣咩位置ok</blockquote><br />\n過左2灘就到布袋澳有個位有得停車，大海景"},{"pid":"df6cd9b473af13971d122d226ef3fce56bc30d7f","tid":378221,"uid":46431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:28:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你都好, 起碼有錢養車<br />\n我都好想有部, 但基層收入, 買部2手每月比幾千閒錢去養都冇能力</blockquote><br />\n我都係萬頭窮撚，月月清。玩車呢d都係玩一年半載了左個心願就賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好羨慕d frd有屋企車/村屋泊車唔洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實平均計埋保險牌費保養，點平都3-5k一個月，如果你供埋車，一個月成皮野支出</blockquote><br />\ncan't agree more <br />\n我認我窮撚，一個月剩幾千就有，但係唔係好捨得<br />\n本身返工地方又唔固定，多數比時租好貴<br />\n有時夜晚返到屋企都七點<br />\n一個